headline: Internet of Things Q3 Earnings: Vontier (NYSE:VNT) is the Best in the Biz
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Vontier (NYSE:VNT) and the rest of the internet of things stocks fared in Q3.
